Use the standard library
This is how to get_closest_vowel of word:
   Remember that vowels is ["a", "e", "i", "o", "u"]
   Remember that best is []
   Remember that best_distance is word's length
   Remember that i is 0

   Do this word's length times:
      Remember that ch is [item i in word]
      When ch is in vowels, then:
         Remember that left is i
         Remember that right is diff of (diff of word's length and 1) and i
         Remember that distance is min of left and right
         When distance is less than best_distance, then:
            Remember that best_distance is distance
            Remember that best is ch
         End when
      End when
      Increase i
   End do

   The answer is best
